codex
The implementation adds an important constraint: `UpdateOverlay` works by finding a parent Scene3D view and creates/reuses a sibling overlay actor; if that parent is absent, it simply leaves the passed actor visible and returns. I’m checking the caller path so the guide doesn’t overstate app-level responsibilities.
